    <item>
      <title>加拿大央行担心就业前景可能延缓消费反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bank-of-canada-worried-jobs-outlook-may-delay-consumer-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行官员越来越担心就业市场疲软可能会延缓消费者支出的复苏，这种担忧促使他们上个月下调了利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bank-of-canada-worried-jobs-outlook-may-delay-consumer-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 17:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 筹集 105 亿美元，为该公司最大规模的高等级债券销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/meta-meta-kicks-off-bond-sale-as-companies-storm-high-grade-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 出售了价值 105 亿美元的投资级债券，这是其有史以来最大规模的债务发行，这将增加其现金储备，因为该公司在人工智能方面投入了大量资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/meta-meta-kicks-off-bond-sale-as-companies-storm-high-grade-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:37:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>史蒂芬·努钦表示是时候取消他创建的新国债了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/mnuchin-says-it-s-time-to-kill-the-new-treasury-bond-he-created</link>
      <description><![CDATA[只要快速浏览一下美国债券曲线，就能发现有些不对劲。有一种美国国债——20 年期国债——与市场其他部分脱节。它的收益率远高于其周边债券——10 年期和 30 年期国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/mnuchin-says-it-s-time-to-kill-the-new-treasury-bond-he-created</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券销售疲软导致交易量震荡，股市停止上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 420 亿美元美国国债抛售后，美国股市迅速下跌，凸显出在历史性动荡之后股市反弹的脆弱性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 22:38:07 GMT</pubDate>
